{"id":255703,"url":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wolfgang_Petersen","text":"Wolfgang Petersen (born 14 March 1941) is a German movie director and screenwriter. His work includes \"The NeverEnding Story\", \"Enemy Mine\", \"Outbreak\", \"In the Line of Fire\", \"Air Force One\", \"Das Boot\", \"The Perfect Storm\", \"Troy\" and \"Poseidon\".\nPetersen was born in Emden, Lower Saxony, Germany. One of his first efforts was the 1977 \"Die Konsequenz\" He worked the 2006 live-action adaptation of the anime movie Paprika.","categories":[],"infobox_types":[],"annotations":[{"uri":"Germany","surface_form":"German","offset":44},{"uri":"Movie_director","surface_form":"movie director","offset":51},{"uri":"Screenwriter","surface_form":"screenwriter","offset":70},{"uri":"The_NeverEnding_Story_(movie)","surface_form":"The NeverEnding Story","offset":103},{"uri":"Enemy_Mine_(movie)","surface_form":"Enemy Mine","offset":128},{"uri":"Outbreak_(movie)","surface_form":"Outbreak","offset":142},{"uri":"In_the_Line_of_Fire","surface_form":"In the Line of Fire","offset":154},{"uri":"Air_Force_One_(movie)","surface_form":"Air Force One","offset":177},{"uri":"Das_Boot","surface_form":"Das Boot","offset":194},{"uri":"The_Perfect_Storm_(movie)","surface_form":"The Perfect Storm","offset":206},{"uri":"Troy_(movie)","surface_form":"Troy","offset":227},{"uri":"Poseidon_(movie)","surface_form":"Poseidon","offset":238},{"uri":"Emden","surface_form":"Emden","offset":270},{"uri":"Lower_Saxony","surface_form":"Lower Saxony","offset":277},{"uri":"Germany","surface_form":"Germany","offset":291},{"uri":"Die_Konsequenz","surface_form":"Die Konsequenz","offset":339}]}